<li><a href="http://direland.typepad.com/direland/2005/07/the_persecution.html" class="external text" title="http://direland.typepad.com/direland/2005/07/the_persecution.html" rel="nofollow">The Persecution of Edgar Morin</a> by Doug Ireland</li>
